data.description: This lovely home has 4 bedrooms and 2 baths that combine modern features to add warmth and elegance, while an open floor plan creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere with fresh paint and luxury flooring throughout. A big kitchen with granite countertops and new top-of-the-line stainless appliances, includes a refrigerator that provides both the space and functionality needed for cooking, dining, and spending quality time together. The delightful patio deck adds a charming outdoor space for morning coffee or summer get togethers. This property also includes an outside storage shed perfect for outdoor equipment. Situated just a few miles from the new Dry River District, and a few miles from Tesla Sub Assembly. Commuting is easy with 1 mile to IH35. Take advantage of this home's optimal location and exquisite features. Don't miss this excellent opportunity; make this lovely house your home. Schedule an appointment today!
